instructions.guide:
设计完整的数据库实体模型

技术栈：MikroORM + TypeScript Decorators

核心实体：
- Project (项目基础信息)
- ProjectAsset (项目资源文件)
- WorkflowGraph (工作流图)
- TaskNode (任务节点)
- TaskOutput (任务产出)

每个实体必须包含：
```typescript
@Entity()
export class EntityName {
  @PrimaryKey()
  id!: string;

  @Property()
  createdAt: Date = new Date();

  @Property({ onUpdate: () => new Date() })
  updatedAt: Date = new Date();
}
```

搭建Vue 3 + Vite前端项目

技术栈：
- Vue 3 (Composition API)
- Vite 7
- TypeScript
- Cytoscape.js (工作流图可视化)

项目配置：
```json
{
  "name": "flow-in-one-frontend",
  "dependencies": {
    "vue": "^3.5.0",
    "cytoscape": "^3.28.0",
    "axios": "^1.6.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@vitejs/plugin-vue": "^6.0.0",
    "typescript": "~5.9.0"
  }
}
```

Vite配置：
```typescript
import { defineConfig } from 'vite'
import vue from '@vitejs/plugin-vue'

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [vue()],
  build: {
    outDir: '../src/public',
    emptyOutDir: true
  }
})
```

实现前后端API对接和数据集成

技术栈：
- Axios (HTTP客户端)
- TypeScript
- Vue 3

API服务层：
```typescript
// src/services/api.ts
import axios from 'axios'

const api = axios.create({
  baseURL: '/api',
  timeout: 5000
})

export const projectService = {
  create: (data: CreateProjectDto) => api.post('/project', data),
  findAll: () => api.get('/project'),
  findOne: (id: string) => api.get(`/project/${id}`),
  update: (id: string, data: UpdateProjectDto) => api.patch(`/project/${id}`, data),
  remove: (id: string) => api.delete(`/project/${id`)
}

export const workflowService = {
  //工作流相关API
}

export const taskService = {
  // 任务节点相关API
}
```

集成组件：
- WorkflowEditor.vue (工作流编辑器主组件)
- 数据双向绑定
- 实时保存功能
-错误处理机制

配置NestJS静态资源服务

技术栈：
- @nestjs/serve-static
- Fastify
- TypeScript

配置要点：

1. App Module配置：
```typescript
@Module({
  imports: [
    ServeStaticModule.forRoot({
      rootPath: join(__dirname, 'public'),
      exclude: ['/api*', '/project*', '/workflow-graph*', '/task-node*'],
      serveRoot: '/public'
    }),
    //其他模块
  ]
})
export class AppModule {}
```

2. Nest CLI配置：
```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "assets": ["**/*.sql", "public/**/*"],
    "watchAssets": true
  }
}
```

3.访路径：
-前端页面：http://localhost:5000/public/index.html
- API文档：http://localhost:5000/api-reference
- API端点：http://localhost:5000/api/project

执行端到端功能测试验证

测试范围：
1. 项目管理功能
2.工作流图创建和编辑
3. 任务节点配置
4.前后端数据同步
5. 用户界面交互

测试用例：
```typescript
describe('Workflow Functionality', () => {
  it('should create a new project', async () => {
    const response = await request(app.getHttpServer())
      .post('/project')
      .send({ name: 'Test Project', description: 'Test Description' });
    expect(response.status).toBe(201);
  });

  it('should render workflow graph editor', async () => {
    const response = await request(app.getHttpServer())
      .get('/public/index.html');
    expect(response.status).toBe(200);
    expect(response.text).toContain('FlowInOne');
  });
});
```
